he will take the fall.

856
01:02:40,290 --> 01:02:42,417
You got it?

857
01:02:42,458 --> 01:02:44,551
And you are my dog now too.

858
01:03:46,122 --> 01:03:48,249
So here's the deal.

859
01:03:48,291 --> 01:03:52,193
