Well, I'm a Leo.

993
01:14:11,814 --> 01:14:14,009
Yeah, I don't know yet.

994
01:14:14,049 --> 01:14:16,040
Why? Why?

995
01:14:16,085 --> 01:14:17,712
Because the fucking fight just ended.

996
01:14:17,753 --> 01:14:20,779
